Static Keyword

1) Static variables and methods are shared across all the objects.
2) Static variables and methods can be directly accessed through class name, without creating any object.



Important points to remember about STATIC:--

1) Static methods can access only static stuff (Direct)- without any object creation
2) Static method can also access the Non-static stuff, but through object creation
3) Non-static methods can access everything(static & non-static with direct access)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Methods	        Static variable				Static method 				non-static variable				non-static method
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
static-method		YES							YES						YES(Through object)				YES(Through object)

non-static method	YES							YES							YES									YES

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------











